{"tid":349342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（抵死）支那扮納粹比人告","createTime":"2017-08-06T13:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T15:05:38.000Z","uid":31181,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"94fbdb46a2a6caa207af33a7df65da495dc22654","tid":349342,"uid":31181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T13:03:02.000Z","msg":"濕鳩翻譯:<br />\n<br />\n有兩隻中國狗因為係柏林做納粹手勢比人拉左<br />\n<br />\n佢地已經比左500歐紙做保釋金所以暫時係得到自由<br />\n<br />\n因為係德國模仿有關希特拉同納粹既言論或動作會係犯法，所以佢地(一個36一個49)有機會<span style=\"color: red;\">罰款</span>或<span style=\"color: red;\">坐三年或以上監</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-40842853\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-40842853&d=fXcoo2K8GYl0vMm88S1Lmo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=aa672ba8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-40842853&h=e7eabb1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-40842853</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：準備考ielts，睇新聞學英文，想分享一下香港唔會提及既新聞<br />\n<br />\n有翻譯錯請屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d583a2252e8e4f28a13fa2e37dabc67aa8c2d5","tid":349342,"uid":21423,"like":9,"dislike":11,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T13:05:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3561c5ee6adb913c4dc326153027eec8225cfa41","tid":349342,"uid":20170,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T13:18:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">比人<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>俾人</strong></span><br />\n左<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>咗</strong></span><br />\n比<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>畀</strong></span><br />\n係<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>喺</strong></span><br />\n既<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>嘅</strong></span><br />\n地<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>哋<br />\n建議也同時學好中文。</strong></span><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://i.imag.cx/XpxKG.png[img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FXpxKG.png%5Bimg%5D&d=fXcoo2K8GYl0vMm88S1Lmo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=a885de38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://i.imag.cx/XpxKG.png[img]</a></span></blockquote><br />\n既然有「也」 就唔需要用「同時」 反之亦然<br />\n語法上屬句子成分贅餘<br />\n建議肥絲學好中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e193f6750deaf4bd9bc72c01123f4da29a4269de","tid":349342,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T13:24:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ee86f7bff86a103ebd1ed39cd4cc88498f9ef69","tid":349342,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T13:25:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20ba8f81e165e1f2ab9268691087830c930654d4","tid":349342,"uid":20170,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T13:35:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔該唔好狗屎垃圾都嚟挑戰啦</blockquote><br />\n有歧義 指：唔好狗屎垃圾「嘅嘢」 抑或：狗屎垃圾「嘅人」？<br />\n語法上屬語意不清<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5419be2b5fcb2d0b66365ecc6f2e5398f0afcc9e","tid":349342,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T13:36:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4e5ce35f04c9582331d57b7ae3a5f5935d3fd7c","tid":349342,"uid":43266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T13:37:54.000Z","msg":"對答案。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1346572-20170806.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1346572-20170806.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=fXcoo2K8GYl0vMm88S1Lmo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=fb485250\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1346572-20170806.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4c22749e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1346572-20170806.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"7bb875463e8229a60c30491e247f52f3c